               <msContents>
                  <summary>Pauline EpistlesPaul’s Epistles. Petrus Aethiops, editor, Testamentum Novum cum epistula Pauli ad Hebraeos (Rome, 1548), and Epistulae XIII divi Pauli (Rome, 1549). F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>–13r: Romans. Tedros Abraha, La Lettera ai Romani Testo e commentary della versione Etiopica, AF 57 (Wiesbaden: Harrassowitz, 2001). <locus target="#13r">13r, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in Romans: ቃሉ ፺ወ፬ ወ ምዕራፉ ፲.  F<locus target="#13r">13r, </locus>–26r: 1 Corinthians. F<locus target="#26r">26r, </locus>–34r:  2 Corinthians. F<locus target="#34r">34r, </locus>–37v: Galatians. F<locus target="#37v">37v, </locus>–41v: Ephesians. Siegbert Uhlig and Helge Maehlum, Novum Testamentum aethiopice: die Gefangenschaftsbriefe, AF 33 (Stuttgart: Franz Steiner Verlag, 1993). F<locus target="#41v">41v, </locus>–44v: Philippians. Siegbert Uhlig and Helge Maehlum, Novum Testamentum Aethiopice: die Gefangenschaftsbriefe, AF 33 (Stuttgart: Franz Steiner Verlag, 1993). <locus target="#44v">44v, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in Philippians: ቃሉ ፪፻፲ወ፪ ወምዕራፉ ፯. F<locus target="#44v">44v, </locus>–47r: Colossians. Siegbert Uhlig and Helge Maehlum, Novum Testamentum Aethiopice: die Gefangenschaftsbriefe, AF 33 (Stuttgart: Franz Steiner Verlag, 1993). <locus target="#47r">47r, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in Colossians: ቃሉ ፫፻፲ወ፬ ወምዕራፈ [፬]. F<locus target="#47v">47v, </locus>–50r: 1 Thessalonians. <locus target="#50r">50r, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in 1 Thesselonians: ቃሉ ፪፻፲ወ፪ ወምዕራፉ ፯. . F<locus target="#50r">50r, </locus>–51v: 2 Thessalonians. <locus target="#50r">50r, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in 2Thesselonians: ቃሉ ፹ ወምዕራፉ ፭. F<locus target="#51v">51v, </locus>–54v: 1 Timothy. <locus target="#54v">54v, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in 1 Timothy: ቃሉ ፫፻ ወምዕራፉ ፳፯. F<locus target="#54v">54v, </locus>–57r: 2 Timothy.  <locus target="#57r">57r, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in 2 Timothy: ቃሉ ፻ወ፯: ወምእራፉ ፪. F<locus target="#57v">57v, </locus>–58r: Titus.  <locus target="#58r">58r, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in Titus: ቃሉ ፯ ወ ምዕራፉ ፭. <locus target="#58r">58r, </locus>-59r: Philemon. Siegbert Uhlig and Helge Maehlum, Novum Testamentum Aethiopice: die Gefangenschaftsbriefe, AF 33 (Stuttgart: Franz Steiner Verlag, 1993). <locus target="#59r">59r, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in Philemon: ቃሉ ፯ ወ ምዕራፉ ፪. F<locus target="#59r">59r, </locus>–67v: Hebrews. <locus target="#67v">67v, </locus> comments on strophes and chapters in the Book of Hebrews: ቃሉ ፫፻፵ወ፯ ወ ምዕራፉ ፳ወ፫. F<locus target="#68r">68r, </locus>-98v: The Acts of the Apostles, ግብረ፡ ሐዋርያት። See, Curt Niccum for text. The Bible in Ethiopia: Book of Acts.
 <locus target="#98v">98v</locus>: Note of ownership, Ato ዛንጅር WITH</summary>
